== Description ==
toggleConsole is a small script which add // (or remove // depends of your choice ) in front of each line which contain a log message.

== Installation ==
Just download the file and execute it ( php toggleConsole.php PARAM ).

== Usage ==
toggleConsoleLog TYPE SOURCE TARGET

- TYPE:
On => turn on console logging
Off => turn off console logging

- SOURCE => path to the dir of file

- TARGET => path to the dir where we store the output. If the dir doesn't exist, the programm try to create it

